channel.title: Library not syncing?
channel.description:
Hi there,
I recently realised whilst looking for recent objects by @SirSickSik & @philoop that the library isn't syncing for me anymore, since about Sept 29th. It's not showing an error when I try either, just says "Sync Successful : factory (1.0.12,anon)"
I'm running Axoloti 1.0.12 on Mac OS 10.12.6
Any ideas what might be going wrong here?
